text: Inés Alder (born 30 April 1970) is an Argentine cross-country skier. She competed in four events at the 1992 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Argentine female cross- country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Argentina Category:Cross-country skiers at the 1992 Winter Olympics Category:People from Bariloche
